title: Mr Bean - AMK Hub
description: Part of soy beverages and snacks chain. Offers a variety of flavored soy milk, tapioca pearl milk, soy ice cream, as well has mini pancakes with filling. Not sure if all vegan - please ask. Dec 2012 reported to have added choice of tuna filling.
streetAddress: 53  Ang Mo Kio 3, #B2-26 Ang Mo Kio Hub
